  <brief_title>Chemoradiation Plus Weekly c225 Against Locoregionally Advanced Nasopharyngeal Carcinoma (NPC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>IMRT With Concurrent Chemotherapy and Cetuximab Against Locoregionally Advanced NPC: a Phase 1 Study</official_title>
