  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will add weekly cetuximab (c225) to the standard care of chemoradiation
      against locoregionally advanced Nasopharyngeal Carcinoma (NPC), and evaluate the toxicity and
      efficacy of this new regimen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
